# Logs
logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
lerna-debug.log*

# Diagnostic reports (https://nodejs.org/api/report.html)
report.[0-9]*.[0-9]*.[0-9]*.[0-9]*.json

# Dependency directories
**/node_modules/
jspm_packages/

# TypeScript cache
*.tsbuildinfo

# Optional npm cache directory
.npm

# Optional eslint cache
.eslintcache

# Optional stylelint cache
.stylelintcache

# Output directories
**/dist/
**/dist-electron/
**/out/
**/target/
**/build/

# IDEs and editors
.idea/
.vscode/
*.suo
*.ntvs*
*.njsproj
*.sln
*.sw?

# OS metadata
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Local env config (保留 .env.example 作为模板)
**/.env
**/.env.local
!**/.env.example

# 一键启动脚本的运行日志
.devlogs/

# Workspace generated documents
**/documents/
**/sqlite.db
**/iml-work.db
**/iml-work.db-journal
**/iml-work.db-shm
**/iml-work.db-wal
docs/

# 客户端运行时认领分身时落盘的技能文件（SKILL.md），非源码，属产物
iml-work-client/skills/

# 沙箱离线 wheel 包：放本地项目、供离线 build，但不进仓（体积大）。保留 .gitkeep 占位目录。
iml-work-admin/admin-backend/docker/sandbox/wheels/*
!iml-work-admin/admin-backend/docker/sandbox/wheels/.gitkeep

# 离线镜像 tar（docker save 的沙箱/docling 镜像）：放本地项目供部署 docker load，太大不进仓。
iml-work-admin/admin-backend/docker/offline/*.tar
!iml-work-admin/admin-backend/docker/offline/README.md
